Kaduna State Universal Basic Education Board (KADSUBEB) has advised teachers that sat for its staff Evaluation Test in December, 2021, to access their Evaluation Test Results by visiting *www.kadsubebtest.com*. A statement issued by KADSUBEB said that teachers can check and print result slips by using either their employee staff number or salary account number, especially the one they used for the evaluation test. KADSUBEB also warned teachers and the general public of fake Competency Test Results that are currently being circulated by some unscrupulous elements. ‘’The Board hereby warns teachers and the general public to be wary of such results from fraudsters and scammers, who are out to defraud unsuspecting teachers,’’ the statement added. 